org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.attachment
Class AeAttachmentFile

java.lang.Object
  java.io.File
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.attachment.AeAttachmentFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable, java.io.Serializable
public class AeAttachmentFile
extends java.io.File

Implements a file managed by an AeFileAttachmentStorage. Maintains a reference count to automatically delete the underlying disk file when the storage and all attached streams are done with the file.
